				</simpara></listitem>
				<listitem><simpara>
					The new subcommand <command>update-check</command> has been added to <command>univention-app</command> to check whether an UCS update with the currently installed Apps is possible (<u:bug>52771</u:bug>).
				</simpara></listitem>
				<listitem><simpara>
